26
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:06,860
Why do you
have to take all this trouble?

27
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:10,900
If Mu Xuanjue dies at the hands of me,

28
00:01:11,300 --> 00:01:12,860
I'll be blamed

29
00:01:13,220 --> 00:01:15,100
