makes you think you can play with power

47
00:03:21,300 --> 00:03:22,660
and do political fights

48
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:24,700
as how you play house.

49
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,860
You're too narcissistic.

50
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:28,740
Sadly, anyone narcissistic

51
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:30,860
