52
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:32,980
Speaking of narcissism,

53
00:03:34,020 --> 00:03:36,260
I do far worse than you, Your Majesty.

54
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,260
Mu Xuanjue,

55
00:04:04,740 --> 00:04:06,140
all this time,

56
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:08,860
I've never loved you.

57
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:13,980
You've been deceiving me all the time.

58
00:04:15,100 --> 00:04:15,780
Today,

59
00:04:16,780 --> 00:04:18,660
I'll make you pay.

60
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:33,380
We're literally perfect for each other.

61
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:02,620
Your Majesty, Consort Ling made it.

62
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:05,500
Good. Get rid of his body.

63
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:06,220
Yes.

64
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:06,980
Come on.

65
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:30,500
Your Majesty.

66
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:33,300
Lingzhi, you did a good job.

67
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:36,700
I'll make good on my promise.

68
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,100
This is the official offer.

69
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:44,980
The day I take the throne,

70
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:48,140
you'll be the first female general.

71
00:05:49,580 --> 00:05:50,620
Thank you, Your Majesty.

72
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,540
Spread the news

73
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:59,740
that the lascivious emperor Mu Xuanjue
was killed by his consort.

74
00:06:00,180 --> 00:06:01,660
The day I take the throne,

75
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:03,540
I'll execute this sinister woman.

76
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:04,900
Yes.

77
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:07,100
Your Majesty, did you get it wrong?

78
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:13,580
I'm asking for a reward
for saving the emperor.

79
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:30,940
Mu Xuanjue?

80
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:33,820
What... What is going on here?

81
00:06:39,420 --> 00:06:40,460
Since then,

82
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:42,900
we've had a plan.

83
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:45,260
We pretended to kill each other

84
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:47,060
for a love-hate relationship.

85
00:06:47,780 --> 00:06:48,980
Stick to my plan.

86
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:50,540
Trust me.

87
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:52,620
I'll give you the answer you want.

88
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:57,220
The Snow King pretended to help

89
00:06:57,580 --> 00:06:58,980
just to take further action

90
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:01,380
and kill your personal guards.

91
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:15,620
It's a good show.

92
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:19,620
The bodies of your guards

93
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:23,300
and the official offer you wrote

94
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:24,860
in the name of the Empress

95
00:07:25,620 --> 00:07:28,900
will prove your crime
of killing the emperor for power.

96
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:32,380
I'll kill you and eliminate

97
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:33,500
all the evidence!

98
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:35,020
Somebody.

99
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:38,140
The imperial guards take orders from me.

100
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:39,980
Somebody!

101
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:41,140
Somebody!

102
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:42,620
Where are they?

103
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:45,580
I'm afraid your personal guards

104
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,740
