of the Spirit clan.

112
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:27,700
You...

113
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:28,380
Yes.

114
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:29,380
I dare you!

115
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:33,500
What?

116
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:36,220
What happened then...

117
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:39,020
You know about it, huh?

118
00:08:40,540 --> 00:08:42,180
Sadly, after all the plots,

119
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:46,540
