120
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:47,700
Shut up!

121
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,900
My plan

122
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:54,140
was indeed flawless.

123
00:08:57,500 --> 00:08:59,140
You killed my mother

124
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:01,380
and framed the Princess
of the Spirit clan

125
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:04,460
just to make me fight the Spirit clan.

126
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:08,220
My mother went to the Spirit clan
for an offer of marriage.

127
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:10,980
You had someone kill my mother,

128
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:12,180
disguised as Princess Shuoye,

129
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:15,020
to start a war between the two clans.

130
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:18,140
I refused
to hurt the people of the Spirit clan.

131
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:22,740
Then your men exterminated them

132
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:25,740
