138
00:09:46,620 --> 00:09:48,140
How can a coward like him

139
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:49,620
be the emperor of the humans?

140
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:52,340
And you cheap alien clans

141
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:53,500
